    <item>
      <title>中国社交媒体对特朗普复出表示钦佩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/chinese-social-media-buzzes-with-admiration-for-trump-s-comeback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国社交媒体用户对唐纳德·特朗普的惊人总统复出表示欢迎，但同时也承认共和党的政治复兴可能意味着世界第二大经济体将面临更多动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/chinese-social-media-buzzes-with-admiration-for-trump-s-comeback</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 05:39:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克反对派领导人放弃重返抗议的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/mozambican-opposition-head-scraps-plan-to-return-before-protest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克反对党领导人放弃了周四返回进行最后游行的计划。该领导人的支持者因上个月有争议的选举而举行抗议活动，震惊了整个东南非国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/mozambican-opposition-head-scraps-plan-to-return-before-protest</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 05:20:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
